# Per-Dockerfile ignore for frontend/Dockerfile (BuildKit prefers this over
# the root .dockerignore, which excludes frontend/** because it serves the
# API image). Allow-list style: exclude everything, re-include what the
# frontend build needs, then carve out heavy or secret subpaths.
**

!package.json
!package-lock.json
!frontend/**

frontend/node_modules/**
frontend/.next/**
frontend/.env
frontend/.env.*
frontend/todo.md
**/.DS_Store
